{
  "name": "Earth Release Partial Assimilation Cylinder",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Earth.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you cast this Jutsu, and as an Action on following turns for its duration you can form a cylinder 10 Feet in diameter and 25 feet long by using chakra to generate molecule sized earth particles. Anyone in the cylinder will begin to be deconstructed on a molecular level. Creatures that start their turn within this cylinder must make a Dexterity Saving Throw. On a failure a creature takes 14d10 Force Damage. If a creature is reduced to less than ½ of their hit points by this damage the user decides on which appendage the target creature lost. (Arm or Leg). If a creature is reduced to 0 Hit Points, they are turned to dust and are immediately killed.</p>",
